ATTACK

Usage: attack <target>

Use this command to initiate an attack against a visible target in the same
room. If you are wielding a weapon it will be used; otherwise you fight
unarmed. Combat follows the game's real-time/tick rules and uses your
skills and stats to determine success.

If you succeed, you will enter active combat and enemy behavior may change.
Use 'wield', 'unwield', 'dodge', and 'parry' to adjust tactics.
